9.4 DUIM-Frames Module

<application-exited-event>

Sealed instantiable class

Summary

The class of events signalled when an application exits.

Library

duim-frames

Module

duim-frames

Superclasses

<frame-exited-event>

Init-keywords

None.

Description

The class of events signalled when an application exits. An instance of this class is distributed when your application is exited, for instance by choosing File > Exit from its main menu bar.

Operations

None.

See also

exit-frame, page 785

<frame-exited-event>, page 798
